g.text: asks to see the irrigation system controller simulation
asks the user to import a file with the irrigation plan or imports one by default
chooses the desired option related to the file with the irrigation plan data
asks the user to input a date/time slot to check if the system is on or asks if the user wants to check the current status
chooses the desired option related to the date/time slot
shows that the system is on, what's the currently irrigated sector and how many minutes left to end irrigation of said sector
shows that the system is off, the next irrigation's details and when it will start (if there's any)
shows if the file was created successfully or not
